column5: I'm having a hard time finding a retailer in the GTA west that sells interstate marine batteries. Anyone know who out in west end sells these?  Thanks in advance
Not sure about the west,I sell'em in the east gta
Drive to any private repair garage and it's probably what you'll find there... May not have a Marine in their stock.. but the truck usually makes rounds weekly and they can get one/two.
Where exacty are you?  I need a new battery this year.
Just bought a nautilus battery from ct today....1000mca and 115 reserve min,,,112 bucks!,,,not a bad price!!
Fishing World in Hamilton used to carry them-give them a shout.
Theirs a dealer at 50 and hiway 7
